headline: Paychex Schedules Second Quarter Fiscal 2026 Earnings Conference Call on December 19, 2025
summary: ROCHESTER, N.Y., December 05, 2025--Paychex, Inc. (Nasdaq: PAYX), an industry-leading human capital management ("HCM") company, will release financial results for its fiscal 2026 second quarter ended November 30, 2025 on Friday, December 19, 2025, before the financial markets open.
